This home has a large kitchen that opens to the spacious living room, formal dining, office, huge WIC in master suite, new laminate in dinning room and carpet, 2 huge outbuildings.  Oversized back deck and covered front deck.  The 40x40 shop next to the home has 400amp service and garage door opener.  The shop behind the home is 40x30 has a concrete floor.
